Reasoning: The paper describes a sensing system for robot manipulation, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses optimization of the sensor design, which could fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of optical time-of-flight range measurement modules and optimization of the elastomer-air boundary could also fall under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper provides hardware design files and software sources, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
